snippet.title: Atomic Butcher Teaser Trailer 1080p
snippet.description:
Blood! Gore! Preposterous acts of violence! Retro, post-apocalyptic platforming action at its finest. Watch this teaser with a little bit of gameplay, because it is good!

Special thanks go to Alexandru Ichim for video editing, and Vincent Wagner for the music.
